<script>!function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js";fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document,"script","twitter-wjs");</script></div>
<div class="Section_B_Photo"><img src="images/michel.jpg" alt="" width="603" height="384" /></div>
	<div class="Section_B_Text">If you know about Atlas, it's because of Michel: the man behind the demand. Across a variety of industries, Michel has always been focussed on one thing: Making a real difference in people's lives. It started with story telling. Michel began his career in the film industry as producer, where he had several successful indie films, including one starring "Social Network" lead, Jesse Eisenberg have won numerous awards and accolades. As the founder of boutique digital agency, Mingling Media, created and managed numerous web, mobile, social maedia and video projects for businesses and brands of all sizes. Using his passion for marketing, Michel heads up Atlas' marketing and business development relationships. Michel is also an accomplished yoga teach. Michel uses Atlas to schedule yoga time and pester Hunter with cryptic tasks.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="Section_A">
<div class="Section_AB_1">
	<div class="Section_A_Header"><img src="images/header_richard.jpg" alt="" width="776" height="149" /></div>
    <div class="Section_A_twitter"></div>
<div class="Section_A_Photo"><img src="images/richard.jpg" alt="" width="603" height="385" /></div>
	<div class="Section_A_Text">Richard aka "Magneto" is a seasoned CTO with a multitude of successful projects behind his belt. Having successfully built software for Microsoft, Bank of America, Ernst &amp; Young, Disney and many others, Richard was looking for the next big technological challenge and saw Atlas as an opportunity to directly impact millions of consumer-users like never before. When not coding, designing frameworks, or researching the newest open libraries, you can find Richard flying RC Choppers or hanging by his home on the beach.</div>
</div>
